Create Maven Project:
 For that: go to file-new-other-maven project-check 'create simple project'-group-id-Artifact-Id-Finish:
 Select working set: deselect all first and then create a new set and add newly created project in that set.
 Adding cucumber dependencies: Go to the following link : https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/io.cucumber/cucumber-java/7.14.0
 copy the dependencies and mention it in pom.xml
 Write features files in src/test/resources
 write stepdefinitions in src/test/java
 Add Selenium dependencies in pom
 
 TestRunner class not present error:
 Right click on project -> Run as -> Maven clean
 Right click on project -> Maven -> Update Project
 
 POM:
 
 Hooks
 